## UI Guidelines

### Color Palette
- Primary Background: `Color(0xFF0A1929)` (Dark blue background)
- Secondary Background: `Color(0xFF1E2A3A)` (Lighter blue for fields)
- Accent Color: `Color(0xFF4CAF50)` (Green accent)
- Text Input Background: `Color.fromARGB(255, 145, 236, 247)` (Light cyan)
- Text Colors:
  - Primary Text: `Colors.white`
  - Secondary Text: `Colors.grey`
  - Input Text: `Colors.black87`
  - Input Hint: `Colors.black54`
- Button Colors:
  - Primary: `Color.fromARGB(255, 71, 214, 93)` (Success green)
  - Secondary: `Colors.grey`
  - Danger: `Color.fromARGB(255, 214, 71, 71)` (Error red)
  - Warning: `Color.fromARGB(255, 214, 118, 118)` (Light red)

### Typography
- Default Text: 16px, white color
- Title Text: 18px, bold weight
- Input Labels: 14px, black87 color
- Button Text: 14-16px, white color
- Small Text/Hints: 12px, grey color

### Layout & Spacing
- Standard Padding: 16.0 pixels (EdgeInsets.all(16.0))
- Content Padding: 12.0 pixels for input fields
- Vertical Spacing:
  - Between Major Sections: 20.0 pixels
  - Between Related Elements: 10.0 pixels
  - Between Form Fields: 8.0 pixels
- Horizontal Spacing:
  - Between Buttons: 16.0 pixels
  - Between Icons: 8.0 pixels

### Component Styling

#### Buttons
- Border Radius: 8.0-10.0 pixels
- Minimum Height: Scale with screen (max 25px)
- Padding: symmetric(horizontal: 32, vertical: 16)
- Elevation: Flat design (0 elevation)
- States:
  - Enabled: Full opacity
  - Disabled: 0.5 opacity
  - Loading: Show CircularProgressIndicator(strokeWidth: 2)

#### Text Fields
- Border Radius: 8.0-10.0 pixels
- Fill Color: Light cyan (`Color.fromARGB(255, 145, 236, 247)`)
- Border: OutlineInputBorder
- Padding: EdgeInsets.all(12)
- Label Style: black87 color
- Hint Style: black54 color

#### Cards & Containers
- Border Radius: 12.0 pixels
- Border: 2px width when used
- Background: Primary background color
- Shadow: Minimal or none (flat design)

#### Dialogs
- Background: Primary background color
- Border: 2px width, accent color
- Border Radius: 12.0 pixels
- Width: 80% of screen width
- Padding: 20.0 pixels all around

#### App Bar
- Background: Primary background color
- Elevation: 0 (flat design)
- Icon Color: White
- Height: Standard `kToolbarHeight`

### Responsive Design
- Logo Width: 85% of screen width (max 460px)
- Field Width: Match logo width
- Button Width: Half of logo width
- Element Height: 4% of screen height (max 25px)
- Dialog Width: 80% of screen width

### Icons
- Size: Default 24.0 pixels
- Color: White for light backgrounds, matching text color for dark
- Touch Target: Minimum 48x48 pixels

### Images
- Logo Placement: Centered
- Background Images: 0.1 opacity when used as watermark
- Image Fit: Contain for logos, cover for backgrounds

### Animation
- Duration: Quick transitions (300ms)
- Curve: Standard curves.easeInOut
- Loading Indicators: Circular, 2px stroke width

### Error States
- Error Color: `Color.fromARGB(255, 214, 71, 71)`
- Error Text: Red color, 14px
- Error Icons: Red color, standard size

### Accessibility
- Minimum Touch Target: 48x48 pixels
- Color Contrast: Maintain WCAG 2.1 AA standards
- Text Scaling: Support system font scaling
- Focus Indicators: Clear visual feedback

### Best Practices
1. Maintain consistent spacing throughout the app
2. Use the defined color palette exclusively
3. Implement responsive sizing for all components
4. Follow material design principles for component behavior
5. Ensure all interactive elements have proper hover/focus states
6. Use loading indicators for async operations
7. Implement proper error states for all inputs
8. Maintain consistent typography hierarchy